race.description: 2026 Wagga Gold Cup Carnival Tickets On Sale Mdn Plt
race.comment: JUST HEAR ME OUT (4) gave backers a bold sight fresh, only to be collared late. Is sure to have come on from that and is drawn the A1. Expecting him to go one better. TASSY FOX (9) finds it tough to break through but it certainly hasn't been without trying. Peaking now and should be poised to strike when they straighten. VANTANTE (12) is knocking on the door an is busting to break through. Gets in well with the claim and strips rock-hard fit. Looks a genuine threat. PEERLESS SON (5) is a Pariah gelding on debut for the Dale camp. Readied with a trial and has Heywood piloting. Can make a bright start.
